---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
import TechMarquee from '../components/TechMarquee.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page-hero compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Big agency know-how, a small senior team, and independent talent when the job needs it.</h1>
    <p>RYCM is founder-led, but not built around one pair of hands. The model is practical: senior judgement, direct access, and the right specialist support around the work.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">How we got here</p>
      <h2>Marketing, technology, psychology and hands-on design.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-copy">
      <p>Martin started in agency media before moving through creative, direct marketing, web development, ecommerce and analytics. The tools have changed, but a lot of the early best-practice principles still hold true: do not talk at people, start a conversation.</p>
      <p>Over the years he has grown agencies, devised strategies and managed teams and projects for UK and international brands. These days RYCM works independently with a trusted network of strong specialists.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section package-section">
    <img src="/assets/projects/packaged-martin.png" alt="Martin Marketing Bloke concept packaging" loading="lazy" />
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Founder-led, not precious</p>
      <h2>Useful marketing thinking should feel accessible.</h2>
      <p>The site has a serious job, but the brand can still have wit. RYCM should feel senior, human and direct, not inflated.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TechMarquee />

  <CTASection />
</BaseLayout>
